OL,4,CConservatives with serious questions
OL,5,Cto answer
OL,7,FThe Treasury audit is a mix of the
OL,8,Fgenuinely shocking and the very
OL,9,Fpredictable, with real-world
OL,10,Fconsequences.
OL,12,FTen million people in the UK are set
OL,13,Fto lose their Winter Fuel Payments. A
OL,14,Funiversal benefit introduced by
OL,15,Fanother Labour chancellor in 1997 is
OL,16,Fset to become means-tested.
OL,18,FThe decision will save the new Labour
OL,19,Fgovernment #1.4 billion this winter.
