OL,7,FIn total, Rachel Reeves has identified
OL,8,F#5.5 billions of savings for 2024/25.
OL,9,FAnd beyond that - unfunded projects
OL,10,Fare being ditched.
OL,12,FThe plan for the Stonehenge tunnel has
OL,13,Fbeen scrapped, along with a bypass on
OL,14,Fthe A27 and the Restore Your Railways
OL,15,Fscheme which was supposed to improve
OL,16,Ftransport links and lift economic
OL,17,Fgrowth.
