OL,7,FReform to limit the amount of money
OL,8,Fpeople have to spend on social care in
OL,9,Flater life to #86,000 is also being
OL,10,Fabandoned.
OL,12,FThe policy was postponed until 2025 by
OL,13,Fthe Conservatives. The Treasury audit,
OL,14,Fcommissioned by the new chancellor,
OL,15,Fhas decided a lack of funding makes it
OL,16,F"impossible to deliver".
OL,18,FReeves says these are "incredibly
OL,19,Ftough" but unavoidable choices.
