OL,4,CConservatives with serious questions
OL,5,Cto answer
OL,7,FShe says the audit shows the
OL,8,Fgovernment is over-spending to the
OL,9,Ftune of #22 billion this year, in a
OL,10,Fway no one had realised and the
OL,11,Fprevious government tried to conceal.
OL,13,FAnd the Conservatives do have serious
OL,14,Fquestions to answer.
OL,16,FWhy hasn't enough money been set aside
OL,17,Fto house asylum seekers and process
OL,18,Fthem claims, to subsidise the railways
OL,19,Fand to provide the military and
OL,20,Fcivilian support that was promised to
OL,21,FUkraine?
