OL,12,FThe "hole" is real and the Office for
OL,13,FBudget Responsibility only found out
OL,14,Fabout the extent of the problems last
OL,15,Fweek.
OL,17,FIt has launched a review into what it
OL,18,Fcalls "one of the largest year-ahead
OL,19,Foverspends" outside of the pandemic
OL,20,Fyears.
