OL,7,FThe review will "assess the adequacy
OL,8,Fof the information and assurances"
OL,9,Fprovided ahead of Jeremey Hunt's
OL,10,FBudget in March.
OL,12,FBut not everything can be pinned on
OL,13,Fthe Conservatives. The idea that
OL,14,FLabour would struggle to keep to the
OL,15,Fspending plans they inherited is not
OL,16,Fremotely new.
OL,18,FAnd it is the new Labour government
OL,19,Fthat chose to increase public sector
OL,20,Fpay by #9.4 billion a year more than
OL,21,Fwas budgeted for.
